  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And he built the walls of the house within with boards of cedar,.... For as yet he had only built the stone walls of it without, but now he wainscotted it with cedar boards: and not only them, but ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "both the floor of the house, and the walls of the ceiling; or from \"the floor of the house unto the walls of the ceiling\"; that is, from the floor, including that, to the walls on each side, reaching up to the ceiling, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "he covered them on the inside with wood: of one sort or another, cedar or fir, or both: particularly he ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "covered the floor of the house with planks of fir: which Hiram sent him, 1 Kings 5:8; which is differently interpreted; by Josephus cypress; by others, as the Tigurine version, pine tree wood; it is very probable it was of the cedar kind, and not the floor only, but the ceiling also, 2 Chronicles 3:5. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "covered the floor of the house with planks of fir: which Hiram sent him, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "1 Kings 5:8",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "; which is differently interpreted; by Josephus cypress; by others, as the Tigurine version, pine tree wood; it is very probable it was of the cedar kind, and not the floor only, but the ceiling also, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 3:5",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
